531
00:40:43,760 --> 00:40:44,960
[SPEAKER_01] Kao da sam prvi korisnik.

532
00:40:45,360 --> 00:40:47,920
[SPEAKER_01] Ne znam što bih radio da nemam ovu aplikaciju.

533
00:40:48,159 --> 00:40:48,880
[SPEAKER_01] To je veliki dio mog života.

534
00:40:49,920 --> 00:40:50,639
[SPEAKER_01] iskustva.

535
00:40:50,960 --> 00:41:00,480
