551
00:42:18,960 --> 00:42:21,039
[SPEAKER_01] Rast je bio stvarno organski.

552
00:42:21,119 --> 00:42:23,679
[SPEAKER_01] Mislim, ljudi su pričali svojim prijateljima, objavljivali su.

553
00:42:24,000 --> 00:42:30,719
